      "",
      "ANSWERING:",
      "Yes: repeat the verb. \u559D. (I drink.)",
      "No: \u4E0D + verb. \u4E0D\u559D. (I don't drink.)",
      "",
      "VERB-NOT-VERB PATTERN:",
